---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Investment Strategy">
	<section class="page-header">
		<div class="container">
			<span class="eyebrow">Investment Focus</span>
			<h1>Disciplined Capital for Defence and Defence-Adjacent Sectors</h1>
			<p>Strengthening NATO capabilities and Europe's technological sovereignty through investments in profitable, revenue-generating companies or those with secured commitments.</p>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="thesis">
		<div class="container">
			<div class="section-header text-center">
				<span class="eyebrow">Investment Thesis</span>
				<h2>The rearmament of <span class="outline">Europe</span></h2>
			</div>
			<div class="grid grid-cols-4 thesis-grid">
				<div class="thesis-card">
					<div class="card-glow"></div>
					<span class="card-num">01</span>
					<h4>Structural Growth in Defence Spending</h4>
					<p>European defence budgets are increasing rapidly as NATO commitments rise and nations prioritize national security infrastructure.</p>
				</div>
				<div class="thesis-card">
					<div class="card-glow"></div>
					<span class="card-num">02</span>
					<h4>Technology Transformation of Warfare</h4>
					<p>Modern defence increasingly relies on electronic warfare, satellites, AI, and autonomous systems, necessitating rapid technological deployment.</p>
				</div>
				<div class="thesis-card">
					<div class="card-glow"></div>
					<span class="card-num">03</span>
					<h4>European Strategic Autonomy</h4>
					<p>EU and NATO are prioritizing domestic defence capabilities and resilient supply chains to ensure long-term technological sovereignty.</p>
				</div>
				<div class="thesis-card">
					<div class="card-glow"></div>
					<span class="card-num">04</span>
					<h4>Industrial Capacity Gap</h4>
					<p>European supply chains must scale quickly to support modern defence systems, creating significant opportunities for industrial expansion.</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="criteria">
		<div class="container">
			<div class="section-header">
				<span class="eyebrow">Investment Criteria</span>
				<h2>What We <span class="outline-dark">Look For</span></h2>
			</div>
			<div class="grid grid-cols-2 criteria-grid">
				<div class="criteria-item">
					<h4>Sector Focus</h4>
					<p>Defence and dual-use technologies across electronic warfare, cybersecurity, satellite communications, UAVs, and smart-weapon subsystems.</p>
				</div>
				<div class="criteria-item">
					<h4>Target Stage</h4>
					<p>Growth-stage and scale-up companies with established products, proven revenue models, and clear commercial offtake — not early-stage or pre-revenue.</p>
				</div>
				<div class="criteria-item">
					<h4>Geography</h4>
					<p>EU and NATO ecosystem, with ownership structures eligible for European Defence Fund participation and aligned with EU and NATO security frameworks.</p>
				</div>
				<div class="criteria-item">
					<h4>Established Operations</h4>
					<p>Profitable businesses or companies with secured government or commercial contracts — revenue-generating with visible and recurring commitment pipelines.</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="params-section">
		<div class="container">
			<div class="section-header">
				<span class="eyebrow">Deal Structure</span>
				<h2>Investment <span class="outline-dark">Parameters</span></h2>
			</div>
			<div class="grid grid-cols-4 params-grid">
				<div class="param-card">
					<span class="param-label">Equity Ticket</span>
					<span class="param-value">€3M – €10M Per Transaction</span>
					<p class="param-desc">Deploying disciplined equity checks into mid-market companies, with capacity to follow on as portfolio companies scale or pursue add-on acquisitions.</p>
				</div>
				<div class="param-card">
					<span class="param-label">Investment Horizon</span>
					<span class="param-value">3 – 7 Year Holding Period</span>
					<p class="param-desc">Structured for patient capital with sufficient runway to drive operational improvements, execute build-and-build strategies, and realise full value at exit.</p>
				</div>
				<div class="param-card">
					<span class="param-label">Governance</span>
					<span class="param-value">Board Seat or Observer Rights</span>
					<p class="param-desc">The fund requires board representation or observer rights at every portfolio company, ensuring meaningful influence over strategic decisions and exit provisions.</p>
				</div>
				<div class="param-card">
					<span class="param-label">Ownership Structure</span>
					<span class="param-value">Controlling or Significant Minority Stakes</span>
					<p class="param-desc">Investments structured as controlling or minority stakes, conditional on securing appropriate governance rights, shareholder protections, and defined exit provisions.</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

</Layout>

<style>
	.page-header { padding-top: 12rem; padding-bottom: 6rem; background: var(--color-secondary); color: var(--color-primary); }

	.page-header .eyebrow {
		display: block;
		text-transform: uppercase;
		letter-spacing: 0.25em;
		font-size: 0.8rem;
		opacity: 0.6;
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
	}

	.page-header h1 {
		font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3rem);
		line-height: 1.1;
		margin: 1rem 0 2rem;
		max-width: 700px;
	}

	.criteria {
		padding: 8rem 0;
		background: var(--color-primary);
	}

	.criteria .section-header { margin-bottom: 4rem; }

	.criteria h2 {
		font-size: clamp(1.75rem, 3vw, 2.5rem);
		margin-top: 0.5rem;
	}

	.outline-dark {
		color: transparent;
		-webkit-text-stroke: 1px var(--color-secondary);
	}

	.criteria-grid { gap: 1.5rem; }

	.criteria-item {
		padding: 2.5rem;
		border: 1px solid rgba(238, 234, 225, 0.08);
		background: rgba(24, 33, 50, 0.3);
		transition: border-color 0.3s ease;
	}

	.criteria-item:hover {
		border-color: rgba(238, 234, 225, 0.2);
	}

	.criteria-item h4 {
		color: var(--color-secondary);
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
		font-size: 1rem;
	}

	.criteria-item p {
		font-size: 0.9rem;
		opacity: 0.65;
		line-height: 1.6;
	}

	.params-section {
		padding: 8rem 0;
		background: var(--color-primary);
	}

	.params-section .section-header { margin-bottom: 4rem; }

	.params-section h2 {
		font-size: clamp(1.75rem, 3vw, 2.5rem);
		margin-top: 0.5rem;
	}

	.params-grid { gap: 1.5rem; }

	.param-card {
		padding: 2.5rem;
		border: 1px solid rgba(238, 234, 225, 0.08);
		background: rgba(24, 33, 50, 0.3);
		transition: border-color 0.3s ease;
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		gap: 0.75rem;
	}

	.param-card:hover { border-color: rgba(238, 234, 225, 0.2); }

	.param-label {
		font-size: 0.75rem;
		text-transform: uppercase;
		letter-spacing: 0.15em;
		opacity: 0.5;
	}

	.param-value {
		font-size: 1.3rem;
		font-weight: 600;
		color: var(--color-secondary);
		line-height: 1.2;
	}

	.param-desc {
		font-size: 0.85rem;
		opacity: 0.55;
		line-height: 1.6;
		margin-top: 0.25rem;
	}

	.thesis {
		padding: 6rem 0 4rem;
		background: radial-gradient(circle at 50% 50%, rgba(238, 234, 225, 0.03) 0%, transparent 70%);
	}

	.thesis-grid { gap: 1.5rem; }

	.thesis-card {
		position: relative;
		padding: 3rem 2rem;
		background: rgba(24, 33, 50, 0.4);
		border: 1px solid rgba(238, 234, 225, 0.05);
		transition: all 0.4s ease;
		overflow: hidden;
	}

	.thesis-card:hover {
		border-color: rgba(238, 234, 225, 0.2);
		transform: translateY(-5px);
		background: rgba(24, 33, 50, 0.6);
	}

	.card-glow {
		position: absolute;
		top: 0;
		right: 0;
		width: 100px;
		height: 100px;
		background: radial-gradient(circle at top right, rgba(238, 234, 225, 0.05), transparent 70%);
		opacity: 0;
		transition: opacity 0.4s ease;
	}

	.thesis-card:hover .card-glow { opacity: 1; }

	.card-num {
		font-family: monospace;
		font-size: 0.8rem;
		color: var(--color-secondary);
		opacity: 0.2;
		display: block;
		margin-bottom: 2rem;
	}

	.thesis-card h4 {
		margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
		color: var(--color-secondary);
		font-size: 1rem;
		line-height: 1.4;
		min-height: 3rem;
	}

	.thesis-card p {
		font-size: 0.9rem;
		opacity: 0.5;
		line-height: 1.6;
	}

	.section-subtitle {
		max-width: 700px;
		margin: 2rem auto 0;
		font-size: 1.1rem;
		opacity: 0.6;
		line-height: 1.6;
	}

	@media (max-width: 1024px) {
		.grid-cols-4 { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); }
	}

	@media (max-width: 640px) {
		.grid-cols-4 { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
		.thesis { padding: 8rem 0; }
	}

	.process {
		padding: 10rem 0; 
		background: #0d121c; 
		background-image: 
			radial-gradient(circle at 2px 2px, rgba(238, 234, 225, 0.05) 1px, transparent 0);
		background-size: 40px 40px;
	}

	.section-header { margin-bottom: 6rem; }
	.eyebrow { 
		display: block; 
		text-transform: uppercase; 
		letter-spacing: 0.2em; 
		font-size: 0.8rem; 
		margin-bottom: 1rem; 
		opacity: 0.6;
	}
	.section-subtitle { 
		max-width: 600px; 
		margin: 2rem auto 0; 
		opacity: 0.7;
	}

	.outline { color: transparent; -webkit-text-stroke: 1px var(--color-secondary); }
</style>
